DESCRIPTION:Seattle Center (1.2 miles NW)\n\nPacific Northwest Ballet perfo
	rms the Romance-period ballet Giselle\, an “ethereal\, haunting\, and tend
	er masterpiece” about love beyond the grave\, at McCaw Hall\, 321 Mercer S
